requestCodes.code:
client = LazopApiClient::Client.new(url, appkey, appSecret)
request = LazopApiClient::Request.new('/product/content/score/get')
request.add_api_parameter("item_id", "692345699")
response = client.execute(request, accessToken)
puts response.success?
puts response.body

client = lazop.LazopClient(url, appkey ,appSecret)
request = lazop.LazopRequest('/product/content/score/get')
request.add_api_param('item_id', '692345699')
response = client.execute(request, access_token)
print(response.type)
print(response.body)
